{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Potato Roly-polies","content":["Place water and 1 tsp salt in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, weigh in potatoes then steam <nobr>30 min\/100°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula, mash potatoes in simmering basket with a fork then leave to cool for 20 minutes. Discard steaming water.","After cooling time, preheat oven to 200°C and line a baking tray with baking paper.","Place shallots and morels in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>6 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter and sauté <nobr>2 min\/120°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add reserved mashed potatoes, egg, cornflour, Taleggio and 1 tsp salt then knead <nobr>45 sec\/<\/nobr>.","On a lightly-floured surface, unroll puff pastry and cover evenly with potato mixture, leaving 3 cm on one long edge, then starting from the other long edge, roll up into a log. Cut the roll into 8 pieces (approx. 4 cm) then place flat on prepared tray.","Bake for 20-25 minutes (200°C) until golden. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl and make dip."]},{"title":"Chive Dip","content":["Place all chive dip ingredients in mixing bowl and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Transfer to a serving bowl and garnish with extra chives (if using). Serve dip with warm potato roly-polies."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Potato Roly-polies","content":["500 g water","2 tsp fine sea salt","330 g floury potatoes, cut in pieces (3 cm)","60 g shallots, halved","15 g dried morel mushrooms, soaked in boiling water for 30 minutes, then squeezed","20 g unsalted butter, diced","1 medium egg","1 Tbsp cornflour","100 g Taleggio cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","275 g puff pastry, ready-rolled","plain flour, for dusting"]},{"title":"Chive Dip","content":["200 g crème fraîche","2 dashes Worcestershire sauce","1 Tbsp lemon juice","½ bunch fresh chives, finely sliced, plus extra for garnishing (optional)","¼ tsp fine sea salt","¼ tsp ground black pepper"]}],"id":"r432803","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-cMSD8tPPrUk\/XZMu5WOo4oI\/AAAAAAAAaLE\/pUyP27RrJosBxY3TOLd9RJlzJ41Qmt2DgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Uno_rq2kqB-W2r_w.png","title":"Potato and Taleggio Roly-polies with Chive Dip","publishedAt":"2019-04-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"21 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"21 g","calories":"1317 kJ \/ 315 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray, baking paper, oven","basicInfo":["medium","15m","1h 10m","8 pieces"]}